Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:03.53,標題,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,470)\pos(1016,444)}藍月的…最終決戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:03.53,標題,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,470)\fs25\pos(953,421)}<Blue Moon·Ragnarok>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能坐起來一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現實世界產生了扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為邪王真眼的力量在弱化…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是有點發燒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要乖乖躺著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 你可是感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天也是硬要出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果馬上就趴在那裡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界已被隱藏…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了 經過一晚的休息 現已全部恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 痊癒之前不准出門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說了 你是想去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這我不能回答 之前就已經說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以漆黑烈焰使之名問汝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:49.20,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(577,660)}<Dark Flame Master>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汝去了哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是要問出來之後採取什麼措施啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是心裡有點不舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花瞞著我去了別的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 很快就真相大白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人 為什麼丟下凸守一個人傷成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,De… De… Death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還沒死啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就能好起來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我願意就可以用邪王真眼的力量來進行恢復 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說要恢復就必須服下 據傳盛開在邪王界暗黑峭壁上的黑龍花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別亂加設定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠太近小心被傳染
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人 請等著我 凸守必定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是害你們被傳染就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦 奇美拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要好好養病哦 作業還沒做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說了禁句…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:04:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為啥！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘記作業就會皺眉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:01.86,註釋,,0000,0000,0000,,發音相似的冷笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 蘇菲婭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾次使用電子協議代碼嘗試與她取得聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:09.28,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(552,660)}<Electr Protocol Code>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但完全沒有現身的跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是… 是嗎 怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙說過最近很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這也太好猜了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七宮說要發動戰爭的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就想著會不會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 丹生谷已經發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一眼就看明白了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她眼裡只有富樫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實是十花小姐說的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那接下來你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能就這樣不管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她可是喜歡你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你突然這麼說我也明白不過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我連交到女朋友都還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼就自暴自棄了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是陳述事實而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是女生比較清楚這種事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我哪會清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就逃了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就別插嘴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於六花的事情也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一有點什麼就馬上…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是看到你們在煩惱才來幫忙的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒求過你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了啦 那隨便你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茴香學姐 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼就別把人家鏟倒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒什麼但是什麼都有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是凸守嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七宮？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇者～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:06:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回歸！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你玩什麼呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個不小心就沒命了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要想克服自我 波紋和魔法能量是非常重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經過這次之後終於全部克服了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後就是魔法魔王少女・改+α外傳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺就像那種越出越爛的遊戲名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是呢 之前那件事已經永遠被丟棄在忘卻之彼岸了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七宮 這樣就好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有天使的反應！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,富樫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會真聽信了剛才那番話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想著已經沒問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只是在逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然知道啊 我跟七宮的交情也不是一兩天的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那叫我怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都說愛情如夢對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然是夢 過一段時間自然就會醒過來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被硬生生叫醒 反而會更加痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茴香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 你管不著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小森大人是太喜歡你們了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:39.58,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(489,660)}<Mori Summer>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡著六花 凸守 富樫 還有七宮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡中二病了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很羡慕你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總想著如果我是中二病就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐您？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就能和你們分享同一種心情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是中二病不是這樣患上的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當你開始憧憬的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就已經是個不折不扣的中二病了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您不是第二代邪王真眼嗎 茴香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.13,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,<Mori Summer>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲婭 你好像很困惑的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這突然是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是記憶恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藥草要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不吃啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是覺得這樣和你溝通更有效
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才特地換了這身衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這衣服很緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲婭啊 我為你帶來了贈言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來自魔術師森大人的贈言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:58.20,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(672,660)}<Mori Summer>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森大人曾與仿冒自己的人戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:02.08,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(442,660)}<Mori Summer>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並作出了懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那時我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要如何面對並戰勝心中的另一個自我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一個自我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 要想瞭解自己 就必須將目光移向外界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如我在與冒牌貨的戰鬥中瞭解了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲婭應該也有必須戰勝的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去尋找那個對手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:29.48,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,<Mori Summer>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屆時 道路自會開闢在你眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻煩 明白我意思了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森大人 謝謝 給你補魔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:43.28,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(471,660)}<Mori Summer>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太近了啦 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 雷霆戰錘 快來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.96,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(583,660)}<Mjolnir Hammer>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不但對漆黑烈焰使下手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:53.29,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(680,660)}<Dark Flame Master>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連冒牌森大人也不放過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:56.30,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(595,660)}<Mori Summer>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好些了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樟葉 月亮出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是漂亮的滿月哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說今夜是Blue Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.15,註釋,,0000,0000,0000,,藍月是不依照規則在日曆中出現的滿月，平均是2.718284年發生一次。\N目前最通俗的定義是出現在一個月中的第二個滿月。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藍月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七宮喜歡我 但是我喜歡六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不明白 太難了 該怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七宮？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇者 不 漆黑烈焰使
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:31.25,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(721,660)}<Dark Flame Master>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要看看我的魔法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七宮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然找了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我戰鬥的對手只有勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能這樣做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是戰爭！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔王認證！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 智音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 六花不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我稍稍離開了一會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七宮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是Blue Moon吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想她是發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就是藍月之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藍月？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暗炎龍？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇者曾經說過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡在自己體內的暗炎龍會再次復甦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要讓它復甦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自久遠的過去走來 永世不變的絕對契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:12:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿越時間 穿越次元
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使去往平行世界的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依舊繼承這份契約
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以絕對力量的姿態 現身在吾面前的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾如今所在的這個混沌的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個迷途誤入的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於那強力的封印之力 以及對記憶的篡改
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正被奪去自己真正的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾恐怕將在不遠的將來 歸為虛無
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以汝啊 吾將力量託付於汝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使吾體內暗炎龍的真實形態降臨於現世的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠將這走入歧途的世界噬盡 變革
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使其涅槃重生的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使暗炎龍復甦的鑰匙有三枚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯庫爾德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.17,註釋,,0000,0000,0000,,北歐神話諾恩三女神中排行第三，掌管“未來”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薇兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:49.14,註釋,,0000,0000,0000,,諾恩三女神中排行第二，掌管“現在”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烏爾德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:52.60,註釋,,0000,0000,0000,,諾恩三女神中排行第一，掌管“過去”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果汝是吾的絕對契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果汝之力量足以與吾生死與共
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集齊這三枚鑰匙應該不費吹灰之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠的契約者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾將等待著那一刻的到來 沉入短暫的安眠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,願汝能在終將降臨的藍月之夜 授予吾力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是藏鑰匙的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然記得不太清 大概就在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在挖著這些…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是邪王真眼放在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是已經挖掘過的標記
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也找過了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼也無法找到的烏爾德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已送往過去的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要將鑰匙送往過去 必須使用平行世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記載在那本筆記上的平行世界的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說要尋找第14座鐵搭的影子的指向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但無從得知是從哪裡開始數的第14座
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以那傢伙就展開地毯式的排查…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 很快就真相大白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙一直為了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道在哪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不太肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對這附近的景色有點印象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你總是那麼認真地對待中二病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是那麼認真地對待戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直為我著想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花 六花 六花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太 這就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烏爾德？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都已經感冒了還在找這種東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,病情加重了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 必須由絕對契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由永遠的契約者來喚醒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是勇太永遠的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定要找到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到它並證明…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不必這麼做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明明是契約者 卻一個鑰匙也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是蘇菲婭卻… 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太是我的契約者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是絕對契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中二那年的夏天骨折了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然埋在了那時的石膏裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真虧當時的我做得出這麼麻煩的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(655,198)\c&H3D3E3C&\fad(200,0)\3c&H80A59D&}水與柱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光這幾個字沒人看得懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在金屬上刻字相當麻煩 中途就放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經過了多少年了竟然還在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是塊石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是喚醒暗炎龍的魔石
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藍月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候查到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是Blue Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 拜託了 邪王真眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾永遠的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爆裂吧 現實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綻開吧 突觸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:35.26,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(703,660)}<synapse>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:41.14,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,<Vanishment this world>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 GelZone UNSAS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是戰爭 讓我和暗炎龍戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我終於明白了 我必須戰勝的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得不打敗的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是與勇者一同掛念 與勇者一同追尋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與勇者一同放棄了的暗炎龍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我必須戰勝的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須做出了斷的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七宮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾名為GelZone UNSAS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是破壞世間一切並將其重築之人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔法魔王少女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永世追求魔法的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我暗炎龍之力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你好好見識一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暗炎龍什麼的根本就不可能存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然也不可能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什… 什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後六花因為感冒加重臥床不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太 追溯時空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓時間回到七月二十號吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應付著處於毀滅性狀態的作業
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迎來了暑假的尾聲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:20:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作業寫不完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢葉要長大了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢葉也要聽電話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前他們叫我去的雅加達最終也沒能去成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的作業沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對新生蘇菲婭來說小菜一碟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七宮結束了和暗炎龍的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進化為新的七宮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊 到底哪裡變了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會變的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠都是魔法魔王少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要以不變之名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將積累之物破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了保持不變而投身有著巨大變化的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是莫非這就是連關天則
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 這就是連關天則
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要去尋找天使嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我說啊 勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
